		<h2 style="padding-left: 20px;" class="whitefont">Need new furniture for your new home:-</h2>

			<p style="margin-bottom: 30px;"> Are you shifting to your new home with completely modern settings or, planning a home renovation?
				Well, in that case, you will need to get completely new furniture for the new place.
				There are many companies and international brands, which sell ready-made furniture in varying sizes and designs,
